This paper deals with the task of detecting stance in tweets, which involves natural language processing and sentiment analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves developing a set of high precision hashtags for each topic, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The use of sentiment lexicons for feature extraction could also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
